text: Reminder to all frontline responders You can find a place to stay with thousands of Airbnb hosts who have opened their homes to those on the frontlines of COVID-19. Sign up for #FrontlineStays now: http://airbnb.com/frontlinestays

In response to the global disruption to travel caused by COVID-19, our Extenuating Circumstances policy now applies globally to all existing reservations with check-in dates between March 14, 2020 and April 14, 2020.
